    <name>Schlotterjoch, 2373 m – Ski touring circuit via Flading in Ratschings</name>
    <desc>Whether you are embarking on an easy or a challenging route with steep slopes and sharp ridge edges depends on the chosen route. The route is popular and scenically magnificent.</desc>
